{"tid":2236102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個行內既秘密","createTime":"2020-10-09T08:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T09:59:23.000Z","uid":242677,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0b8f4ff417f49043476a9b57a58bc165212d1dd7","tid":2236102,"uid":242677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:22:51.000Z","msg":"人人以為香港油價好貴<br />\n事實係岩一半<br />\n因為香港柴油係無稅<br />\n如果有車隊係有大折扣 或者出面入油車油<br />\n5-6蚊一升<br />\n所以香港政府從不想引入柴油私家車"},{"pid":"75029b62786c0e22730b1b5553426d3459152822","tid":2236102,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:25:39.000Z","msg":"呢個叫秘密?"},{"pid":"87ef938f405bce85313deb673204bc179cf8bc29","tid":2236102,"uid":5793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:26:32.000Z","msg":"Dc9從不報稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925902c43e9314916e75c52fcc6f1cb9674c25c2","tid":2236102,"uid":275570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:29:58.000Z","msg":"Asia Miles好垃圾<br />\n<br />\n要儲不如儲其他One World FFP"},{"pid":"8701aef8bc5893cf1e746258f965817bfb520efa","tid":2236102,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:30:10.000Z","msg":"btw 其實都唔洗咩大車隊<br />\n舊公司4架車已經減8個幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0edc9b7b19b83cf198f2ee451c7a62c012f7e581","tid":2236102,"uid":308165,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:30:46.000Z","msg":"社福界好多賤人"},{"pid":"75ccd6aaa85fc0403f5b39a2d87a72a984a60d08","tid":2236102,"uid":378305,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:32:32.000Z","msg":"做雞，黑色西裝友一定係變態西客"},{"pid":"f48206975c670ec553de56d9d7d0fc7a3e9fd6a7","tid":2236102,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:32:54.000Z","msg":"係人都知，本身都減7.幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d205daa3844d7a4dca1733af7d81d8fac2a32d","tid":2236102,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:33:55.000Z","msg":"教畜真係好畜<br />\n一間學校起碼一半人係冗員"},{"pid":"6c4de6cf856b114593f9f3ed1f42150ba3abf27a","tid":2236102,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75029b62786c0e22730b1b5553426d3459152822","tid":2236102,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:25:39.000Z","msg":"呢個叫秘密?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:43:24.000Z","msg":"你知就唔係秘密？<br />\n我而家先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7728bd61b431b3caa4ce95b3bad759cb4218fdc0","tid":2236102,"uid":116705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:43:40.000Z","msg":"地盤管理層冇個好人<br />\n<br />\n安全佬唔係人"},{"pid":"7c459c21c5835b06888c616aa83c503edc74248f","tid":2236102,"uid":103653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:50:47.000Z","msg":"而家油價 電油17.54 我用最高折扣嗰張都係3.X<br />\n折扣之後都仲貴過油渣 <br />\n我老豆張油渣卡去入油價錢減半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要唔使俾稅....<br />\n同埋啲仆街油公司 全部都係合謀定價 呢間做完promote即刻到第二間做 第二間做完就第三間做 無合謀定價搵鬼信"},{"pid":"33ce4488019eb9db0fc5f223aa53739cdfa9b1fc","tid":2236102,"uid":68430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:30:43.000Z","msg":"Googler 係垃圾 從來唔睇客email 唔覆客email 態度差 周圍做freelance吸公司錢"},{"pid":"53708e41e636d92e2e60601a6c245eb7903d22d0","tid":2236102,"uid":190789,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:51:20.000Z","msg":"1)某大品牌戲院比你想像中更污糟，唔會有院內大清潔，啲櫈可能由day one生存到戲院拆，抹唔超過30次<br />\n2)以為裝修完好靚？大部分都係門面功夫，院內變化近乎0(啲櫈拆完再裝返) 因為熄咗燈一樣，但裝修費每次過百萬<br />\n3)你哋食嘅爆谷大部分放係垃圾袋儲存，有啲會用靚少少嘅透明袋，個袋用上百次，有啲袋仲有米奇咬過，只有少部份用箱。<br />\n4)戲院真正獲利係小賣部，你唔洗避開品牌去睇戲支持本土，你入場都會分賬俾片商，唔買嘢食就得。第一個星期永遠最多。<br />\n5)每間劇院都有Hold位，只要投訴合理/發晒脾氣，自然有機會坐，港島西啲位一撚流。<br />\n6)每間戲院嘅死症都係冷氣，好多時鮮風機有事，有時係冷水機有事，半夜尾場好多商場式戲院為咗慳錢，買少1個鐘冷水，所以會好熱。<br />\n7)當戲院無啦啦送你coupon買嘢食，一定係又加價"},{"pid":"52e1084776aad104c9bf9d03553921726b4c6210","tid":2236102,"uid":187664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:52:13.000Z","msg":"HK No IT"},{"pid":"444ecee1f1d6c5dc11c1490a25c3722e9eb4f949","tid":2236102,"uid":242677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52e1084776aad104c9bf9d03553921726b4c6210","tid":2236102,"uid":187664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:52:13.000Z","msg":"HK No IT"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:59:23.000Z","msg":"係人都知"}]}